===Pronunciation===
פּרה / pârâh / paw-raw'

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Noun===
'''פּרה'''

# To bear fruit (literally or figuratively): - bear, bring forth (fruit), (be, cause to be, make) fruitful, grow, increase.

